1948;;Noose;;British;;Edmond T. Gréville;;Carole Landis, Derek Farr;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noose_(film);;Set in post-Second World War Britain, Noose is the story of black market racketeers who face attempts to bring them to justice by an American fashion journalist, her ex-army fiancé and a gang of honest toughs from a local gym. The normally proficient and urbane Nigel Patrick is cast as a cockney spiv.